title: 2nd Floor 1 bedroom +den, pet friendly home with W/D
posting_body: ['Eden Commons is a controlled access, 100% smoke-free community, owned and operated by Bigos Management.', 'We are conveniently located within walking distance of the Eden Prairie Center Mall, as well as the Eden Prairie library.', 'You would have access to our 24 hour fitness center, outdoor pool, and recently renovated clubhouse.', 'SPECIAL:', "Move in by 9/15/22 with a 9 – 13 month lease term & get $1000 off your first month's rent!", 'This Oak layout is a 1 bedroom / 1 bathroom / + den, on the 2nd floor with a full-size washer and dryer, fireplace, big windows, central air, patio, garage and outdoor storage unit.', 'This spacious one bedroom floor plan is available 10/1/22!', 'Dog friendly apartment!', '$40/month per dog, breed restrictions and deposits apply.', 'Cat friendly apartment!', '$15/month per cat, cat rent and deposits apply.', 'We offer 3 to 15 month leases, with rent starting at $1,665.', 'Please call us at', 'show contact info', 'to set up a tour today, or visit <URL>.', 'More options are also available.', 'We look forward to hearing from you!', 'Disclaimer: Pricing is subject to change daily.', 'Adjusting your move-in date or lease term will adjust pricing.', 'Payment of the application fee will lock the rental rate for only the selected lease term and move-in date.', '#922']
